member.name: WS_ANY_ATTRIBUTE
member.summary: This type is used to store an attribute that has not been directly mapped to a field.

member.name: WS_ANY_ATTRIBUTE.localName
member.summary: Specifies the localName of the attribute.

member.name: WS_ANY_ATTRIBUTE.ns
member.summary: Specifies the namespace of the attribute.

member.name: WS_ANY_ATTRIBUTE.value
member.summary: Specifies the value of the attribute. This field may not be NULL.
